Class Vector4

  • java.lang.Object
    • thothbot.parallax.core.shared.math.Vector2

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Vector

    public class Vector4
extends Vector3
implements Vector
    This class is realization of (X, Y, Z, W) vector. Where: X - x coordinate of the vector. Y - y coordinate of the vector. Z - z coordinate of the vector. W - w coordinate of the vector.
    Author:
    thothbot
